SUMMARY:Out & About at Dram & Draught
DESCRIPTION:It’s the first day of spring! We can’t think of a better day to meet some adoptable dogs while you’re kicking back on the patio at Dram & Draught with a delicious cocktail or one of their carefully curated beers on tap. Grab a few friends and head down and see us!
URL:https://www.apsofdurham.org/event/out-about-at-dram-draught-6/
LOCATION:Dram & Draught\, 701 W Main St\, Durham\, NC\, 27701
CATEGORIES:Adoption Events
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://www.apsofdurham.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/0321-Dram-Draught-1.jpg
END:VEVENT
