SUMMARY:Out & About at St. Francis of Assisi
DESCRIPTION:We’re headed just down the road to northwest Raleigh for a celebration of animals\, and what better place for it than St. Francis? APS will be one of several shelters and rescues participating in the event\, and we’ll have a few adoptable dogs for you to meet\, greet\, and fall in love with! See you there!
URL:https://www.apsofdurham.org/event/out-about-at-st-francis-of-assisi/
LOCATION:St. Francis of Assisi Catholic Church\, 11401 Leesville Rd.\, Raleigh\, NC\, 27613
CATEGORIES:Adoption Events
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://www.apsofdurham.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/0322-St.-Francis-of-Assisi.jpg
END:VEVENT
